 ('1', '2', 'en_us', NULL, 'Hello!', '<p>\r\n	  Welcome to the new home of the AU Design Club. We\'re a small group of passionate design student, forming the next generation of DC designers. You can probably find us at the Katzen Arts Center between the hours of midnight and 4 AM, working on projects, singing \"Call Me Maybe,\" and probably crying over AfterEffects. If any of those sound like you, come join us! We meet every Tuesday at 8PM in Katzen 204, and have a wide variety of speakers and events planned for the coming year.\r\n</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2013-06-21 23:58:55', '2013-06-25 18:29:29', '1bf5600d-9df8-4c89-b4e6-8208d5e26572'),
